# OctoFit Tracker Frontend Environment Configuration

# GitHub Codespaces name (required for Codespaces deployment)
# Set this to your Codespaces name when deploying to Codespaces
# Example: my-codespace-name
# For local development, you can comment this out or leave it empty
VITE_CODESPACE_NAME=

# API Configuration
# If VITE_CODESPACE_NAME is not set, the app falls back to localhost:8000
# Codespaces: https://${VITE_CODESPACE_NAME}-8000.app.github.dev
# Localhost: http://localhost:8000
